      <title>C++ Inherited constructor</title>
      <link href="/posts/d1a9.html"/>
      <url>/posts/d1a9.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="继承的构造函数"><a href="#继承的构造函数" class="headerlink" title="继承的构造函数"></a><center>继承的构造函数</center></h1><h2 id="基类-amp-派生类的关系"><a href="#基类-amp-派生类的关系" class="headerlink" title="基类&amp;派生类的关系"></a>基类&amp;派生类的关系</h2><h3 id="1-派生类拥有基类的数据成员和成员函数；"><a href="#1-派生类拥有基类的数据成员和成员函数；" class="headerlink" title="1. 派生类拥有基类的数据成员和成员函数；"></a>1. 派生类拥有基类的数据成员和成员函数；</h3><ul><li><p>派生类在基类的基础上<strong>可实施以下改变</strong>：</p><ol><li>增加新的成员（数据+函数）。</li><li>重载(overload)基类的成员函数。 </li><li>重定义(override,覆盖)基类已有的成员函数。</li><li>改变基类成员在派生类中的访问属性。</li></ol></li><li><p>派生类<strong>不能继承</strong>基类的以下内容： </p><ol><li>析构函数。 </li><li>基类的友元函数。 </li><li>静态成员（数据+函数）  </li><li>针对基类定义的一些特殊运算符，如new等。 基类的构造函数C++11之前不能继承，之后可以继承；</li></ol></li><li><p>基类的构造函数C++11之前不能继承，之后可以继承；  </p></li></ul><h3 id="2-派生类的访问权限"><a href="#2-派生类的访问权限" class="headerlink" title="2. 派生类的访问权限"></a>2. 派生类的访问权限</h3><ul><li><p>派生类继承了基类的所有成员，但派生类能够直接访问从基类继承来的公有和保护成员，且只能通过这两类成员访问从基类继承来的私有成员。</p><ul><li>基类：</li></ul><pre class="line-numbers language-C++"><code class="language-C++">class Base{    base members;};<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>派生类：</li></ul><pre class="line-numbers language-C++"><code class="language-C++">class Derived: public Base{    new members;};<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li></ul><ul><li><p>派生类对基类(子对象)成员的访问形式</p><ol><li>通过派生类对象直接访问基类成员</li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-C++"><code class="language-C++">Derived d;cout&lt&ltd.j;   d.fn2();<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ol start="2"><li>在派生类成员函数中直接访问基类成员 </li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-C++"><code class="language-C++">Derived d;d.fn3();<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ol start="3"><li>通过基类名字限定访问被重载或重定义的基类成员名</li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-c++"><code class="language-c++">Derived d;d.Base::fn1(); <span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p><strong>有关派生类访问权限的例子：</strong></p><pre class="line-numbers language-c++"><code class="language-c++">#include &ltiostream&gtusing namespace std;class Base { //基类public:    int k;      //为演示,将数据成员声明为公有    void fn1(){ cout&lt&lt"Base::fn1()"&lt&ltendl; }        void fn2(){ cout&lt&lt"Base::fn2()"&lt&ltendl; }};class Derived: public Base { //派生类};void main(){ Derived d;    cout&lt&lt"k="&lt&ltd.k&lt&ltendl;    d.fn1();    d.fn2();}<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>上述代码说明： 派生类中没有新增加或者是重定义的成员，派生类Derived 拥有成员：k, fn1(), fn2()，派生类拥有的数据成员和基类是一样的。          </p><pre class="line-numbers language-c++"><code class="language-c++">#include &#60iostream&#62using namespace std;class Base { //基类public:    int k;      //为演示,将数据成员声明为公有    void fn1(){ cout&lt&lt"Base::fn1()"&lt&ltendl; }        void fn2(){ cout&lt&lt"Base::fn2()"&lt&ltendl; }};class Derived: public Base { //派生类public: int m;    void fn3(){ cout&lt&lt"Derived::fn3()"&lt&ltendl; }};void main(){ Derived d;    cout&lt&lt"k="&lt&ltd.k&lt&ltendl;    d.fn1();    d.fn2();    cout&lt&lt"m="&lt&ltd.m&lt&ltendl;   d.fn3();}<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li></ul><script>        document.querySelectorAll('.github-emoji')          .forEach(el => {            if (!el.dataset.src) { return; }            const img = document.createElement('img');            img.style = 'display:none !important;';            img.src = el.dataset.src;            img.addEventListener('error', () => {              img.remove();              el.style.color = 'inherit';              el.style.backgroundImage = 'none';              el.style.background = 'none';            });            img.addEventListener('load', () => {              img.remove();            });            document.body.appendChild(img);          });      </script>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> C++ </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
